text: Bénédicte Evrard (born 21 March 1975) is a Belgian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Brussels
